(28, 1, '2014-04-08 14:07:10', '2014-04-08 14:07:10', '<h1>Regulatory Mastery</h1>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">One of the consequences of the financial crisis has been a tighter regulatory environment and more intense scrutiny, leaving banks and insurers struggling to keep pace with the accelerating introduction of new regulations. \r\n\r\nThis presents many challenges for Risk and Compliance functions. They must interpret new regulations correctly; understand where they should be applied; communicate the required changes across the organization; ensure the changes are made; and demonstrate their existence and effectiveness to the relevant regulator. All while making optimum use of the often limited budget and resources available for compliance initiatives. \r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">With its centralized, portfolio-driven approach, an EPPM solution can enable Risk and Compliance professionals to:\r\n<ul class="list-unstyled custom-list">\r\n	<li>Plan and execute compliance strategies centrally</li>\r\n	<li>Enable full visibility and collaboration around compliance initiatives</li>\r\n	<li>Efficiently manage, allocate and track compliance resources and budgets</li>\r\n	<li>Minimize compliance costs and risks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTo discover more about how EPPM can enable your organization to achieve regulatory mastery in a fast-changing world, browse the resources below.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Regulatory Mastery', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'regulatory-mastery', '', '', '2014-06-30 12:13:41', '2014-06-30 12:13:41', '', 0, 'http://oracle.mointernational-clients.co.uk/?page_id=28', 0, 'page', '', 0),
