(144, 1, '2014-04-30 14:20:12', '2014-04-30 14:20:12', 'It''s easy to view regulations as a cost of doing business but you need to do more than simply comply. You need to develop capabilities that will allow you to thrive in an era of re-regulation. You need to rationalize compliance initiatives to reduce compliance costs, identify opportunities for competitive advantage and develop systems that will allow you to be more agile and respond to new and evolving regulatory initiatives. \r\n\r\nLearn how financial organizations are using project portfolio management to address the following challenges:\r\n<ul class="list-unstyled custom-list">\r\n	<li>Managing the volume of change</li>\r\n	<li>Communication and collaboration among various groups/functions</li>\r\n	<li>Identifying specific projects and milestones</li>\r\n	<li>Competing priorities/projects</li>\r\n        <li>Resource availability or allocations</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Compliance Week OnDemand Webcast - How Project Portfolio Management Can Enable Regulatory Mastery', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'compliance-week-ondemand-webcast-project-portfolio-management-can-enable-regulatory-mastery', '', '', '2014-04-30 14:20:27', '2014-04-30 14:20:27', '', 0, 'http://oracle-eppm.local/fsi/?p=144', 0, 'post', '', 0),
